Interviewer twist:

Prevent soft-deleted tasks from being updated.
PATCH /tasks/:id should return 404 if task is soft deleted.

Modify update logic accordingly.


###

def update
  task = Task.active.find_by(id: params[:id])

  return render json: {errors: "Task not found"}, status: :not_found unless task

  if task.update(task_params)
  else
  	render json: {msg: "Task updated"} 
  end
end